== About
I am interested in building tools and models that make complex systems easier
to understand. My current focus areas include:

- trustworthy machine learning and evaluation;
- numerical methods and optimization;
- developer tools for research workflows;
- clear technical communication and reproducible experiments.

== News
- *May 2026:* Personal website scaffolded with jemdoc+MathJax.
- *Spring 2026:* Add your latest paper, project, internship, award, or talk here.
- *Winter 2026:* Add a concise milestone with a link when available.

== Selected Work
- [/projects.html Research Workflow Toolkit] -- a compact toolkit for reproducible
