== MathJax Check
This page supports numbered equations through MathJax:

\(
\begin{equation}
\min_\theta \; \mathbb{E}_{(x,y)\sim \mathcal{D}}
\left[\ell(f_\theta(x), y)\right] + \lambda \|\theta\|_2^2.
\label{eq:objective}
\end{equation}
\)

Equation $\eqref{eq:objective}$ is a placeholder objective you can replace with
your own research notation.
